com.oose2013.group7.roommates.waitingroom

Class Waitingroom

  • java.lang.Object
    • Activity
      • com.oose2013.group7.roommates.waitingroom.Waitingroom

  • public class Waitingroom
extends Activity
    Main activity for waiting room. The application must run with the server running. It loads files from the server first, then stores them in the sdcard, finally displays it on the screen. If we upload a new photo, the whole activity will be reloaded.
